    .conveyancer
      .media
        img.align-self-center.mr-3(src='//via.placeholder.com/150', alt='Generic placeholder image')
        .media-body
          h5.mt-0 Hi, I’m Rory
          p
            | I’m a conveyancer.
          //- p
          p I’m here to help at ConvX. Contact me anytime and I’ll help you settle your property confidently, quickly and cheaply. We’ve got you covered!
